message: Count me in! I can bring extra gloves and refillable water jugs.
I'll grab pastries from Coffee Drunk to share afterwards.
Anyone need a ride from East Long Beach? I have space for two more volunteers.
Welcome back to the Latte Lounge! Grab any open seat and order before 6:15.
I'll bring a dozen matcha muffins so we have snacks during the first break.
Just posted a lo-fi playlist in chat—perfect background focus when we regroup.
I can draft the expo layout and share it in chat before Thursday.
Count on a hydration station and first-aid kit next to the solar workshop table.
I'll bring extra ND filters if anyone wants to experiment with longer exposures.
Love it. I'll coordinate signage so volunteers can point folks to your booth.
I'll pack a reflector and spare batteries for anyone needing them.
